###  https://w3id.org/ssbd/SustainabilityDimension
ssbd:SustainabilityDimension rdf:type owl:Class ;
                             rdfs:subClassOf ssbd:SSbDDimension ;
                             skos:altLabel "Sustainability Dimension"@en ;
                             skos:definition "The dimension of sustainability in the context of SSbD assessments of chemicals and materials."@en ;
                             skos:prefLabel "SustainabilityDimension"@en ;
                             skos:scopeNote """Sustainability is the state of the global system, including environmental, social and economic aspects, in which the needs of the present are met without compromising the ability of future generations to meet their own need. 
Note 1 to entry:The environmental, social and economic aspects interact, are interdependent and are often referred to as the three dimensions of sustainability.
Note 2 to entry: Sustainability is the goal of sustainable development.
https://www.iso.org/obp/ui/en/#iso:std:iso:guide:82:ed-2:v1:en""" .


